wrapper-generator is a finished eiffel-gcc-xml from Eiffel Wrapper Library Collection.

Mostly working, even if the output is correct it may not be what one would expect from such a tool.

Requirements
SmartEiffel release 2.4 or a snapshot more recent than 9297
gccxml from CVS. If you work on Ubuntu 10.10 or 11.04 then you need version later than 0.9.0+cvs20100501-2 or compile from sources checked out from cvs after 2010-07-14 when they fixed a bug regarding gcc-4.5; Ubuntu 11.10 (Oneiric Ocelot) fixes this

